<html>
<head>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="css/global.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="css/Help.css">
    <title>Help</title>
</head>

<body>
<script id="replace_with_navbar" src="nav.js"></script>


<div id="main-container">

<h2>Having Trouble? Let's do something about that.</h2>

    <div class="faq-header">Frequently Asked Questions</div>

    <div class="faq-content">
        <div class="faq-question">
            <input id="q1" type="checkbox" class="panel">
            <div class="plus">+</div>
            <label for="q1" class="panel-title">What is the return policy?</label>
            <div class="panel-content">For each order it is 45 days from the date the order was placed.</div>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-question">
            <input id="q2" type="checkbox" class="panel">
            <div class="plus">+</div>
            <label for="q2" class="panel-title">How long does shipping take?</label>
            <div class="panel-content">Orders placed within Monday-Wednesday between 8am-5pm should arrive within the next two business days. Any order placed after Wednesday should be delivered by the following Monday or start of the business week. </div>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-question">
            <input id="q3" type="checkbox" class="panel">
            <div class="plus">+</div>
            <label for="q3" class="panel-title">What happens if I receive an incorrect or defective item?</label>
            <div class="panel-content">If you happen to get a damaged/incorrect item within your shipment. Please take a photo of the item or items and include your order number for validation of the order. Afterward, we shall be in contact with you about the next steps to rectify your order within the next several hours.
                Our email is (helpfaq@hikari.com).</div>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-question">
            <input id="q4" type="checkbox" class="panel">
            <div class="plus">+</div>
            <label for="q4" class="panel-title"> What if I have an error with the order that hasn't shipped yet?</label>
            <div class="panel-content"> Please  email us with the order number to create a ticket for your situation. (helpfaq@hikari.com)</div>
        </div>
    </div>

</div>
<script id="replace_with_footer" src="Padfeet.js"> </script>
</body>
</html>
